## PFM Product Overview

PFM (Personal Finance Management) is a core cross-cutting capability within MoneyLion — not a single screen, but a system of features that help users understand and act on their financial picture.

PFM sits within MoneyLion's **"See" pillar**: *Know what's coming before it hits — bills, paydays, shortfalls, safe-to-spend balance.*

PFM features are designed to surface insights that drive action across other MoneyLion products. A low balance insight leads to an Instacash offer. An upcoming large bill surfaces a Split offer. Detecting spending drift triggers a savings nudge. PFM is the intelligence layer — the products are the response.

