## User Stories (Shared Across PFM Features)

### Accounts and Overview
- As a customer, I want to see all of my accounts in one consolidated view so that I can quickly understand my overall financial position.
- As a customer, I want each account to clearly show my current balance, available balance, and Safe to Spend so that I know what portion of my money is truly available.
- As a customer, I want to understand at a glance which accounts are primarily for spending versus saving so that I can use them appropriately.

### Transaction Enrichment and Categorization
- As a customer, I want merchant names and logos to be cleaned and standardized so that I can easily recognize where I spent money.
- As a customer, I want my transactions to be automatically categorized into simple, meaningful categories so that I can understand my spending patterns without doing manual work.
- As a customer, I want to see which transactions are pending versus posted and how they affect my available funds so that I can avoid surprises when they settle.

### Safe to Spend and Forecasting
- As a customer, I want the app to calculate a Safe to Spend amount that subtracts my expected bills and obligations from my balance so that I can safely make discretionary purchases.
- As a customer, I want to see a simple view of upcoming recurring payments and their expected dates so that I can plan my cash flow over the coming weeks.

### Insights and Guidance
- As a customer, I want to receive clear, timely insights about unusual spending, bill changes, or low Safe to Spend so that I can adjust my behavior before issues occur.
- As a customer, I want any insights or alerts to be grounded in simple explanations and clear numbers so that I can trust and act on them.

