## Adding a New PFM Feature

When starting work on a new PFM feature:

1. Add a new `## Feature: [Name]` section to this file following the Cash Flow section format
2. Create `features/[feature-name]/` with: `brief.md`, `design-spec.md`, `phases.md`, `risks.md`
3. Create `prototypes/[feature-name]/` for the React prototype

Do not create a separate workspace or duplicate the four core `.cursor/rules/` files. All PFM features share the same rules infrastructure.

